video.title: Phil Collins has no time for his fans in New York City
video.description: A fan approaches Phil Collins in New York City and asks him if he will autograph his guitar for him. Phil immediately says "No I'm not doing it!" without a second thought. The fan is confused, so he runs up to Phil again and asks him even more politely, saying please and explaining that he's a big fan and it would mean a lot to him. Phil refuses again "Sorry, man" before getting into his waiting car.
